DESCRIPTION Pandoc is a Haskell library for converting from one markup format to
another, and a command-line tool that uses this library. It can read
Markdown, CommonMark, PHP Markdown Extra, GitHub-Flavored Markdown,
and (subsets of) Textile, reStructuredText, HTML, LaTeX, MediaWiki
markup, TWiki markup, Haddock markup, OPML, Emacs Org mode, Docbo...
